#: ../../S/steved.rst:5
msgid "steved"
msgstr "steved"

#: ../../S/steved.rst:7
msgid "adj\\.,v\\., /steevd/"
msgstr "形容詞・動詞, /steevd/"

#: ../../S/steved.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Apple employees and users] Terminated, said of a development project. "
"Originated after Steven P. Jobs returned to Apple as acting CEO in 1997. "
"Jobs immediated axed several development projects, including OpenDoc and "
"Newton that had been launched by John Sculley, the man who had ousted Jobs "
"in the mid 1980s. Now any project shut down at Apple and often at any large "
"firm connected with Apple may be said to have gotten steved. It is usually "
"spelled lowercase despite the origin. It is almost always past-tense and "
"used quasi-adjectivally."
msgstr ""
"[Appleの従業員とユーザー] 終了させられた。開発プロジェクトについて言われる。Steven P. "
"Jobsが1997年に暫定CEOとしてAppleに復帰した後に生まれた。Jobsは即座に、1980年代半ばにJobsを追放した男John "
"Sculleyが立ち上げたOpenDocやNewtonを含むいくつかの開発プロジェクトを切り捨てた。今やAppleで、そしてしばしばAppleと関係するどんな大企業でも、打ち切られたプロジェクトはstevedされたと言われうる。由来にもかかわらず通常は小文字で綴られる。ほぼ常に過去形で、準形容詞的に使われる。"
